Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 8.5%, while daily reported deaths have decreased by 10.2%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show a 28.6% decrease in daily reported cases and a 15.3% decrease in reported deaths.

Impression: The global daily report registered over 1.74 million newly confirmed infections in the past 24 hours with over 455.51 million cumulative reported cases and more than 6.05 million reported deaths. - Mod.UBA

